{"tid":246081,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲鍾意食辣","createTime":"2017-05-16T17:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T18:19:13.000Z","uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2691081cb57aeea6c131c1526f15332680934f23","tid":246081,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都好鍾意食辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左18年 食嚟食去都係麻辣米線 麻辣火鍋 麻辣乜乜乜 食都食到悶<br />\n我想試下新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴絲介紹食辣既好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好就係九龍區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過其實我食辣會敏感 塊面會出紅點 然後塊面會腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2f7ff5d2e94fbb92ffd28c24a857d42659ec23","tid":246081,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"為左食辣變豬頭柄都肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e6eaabeca2be3cd810a537dd4e06b0ca024c9","tid":246081,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左食辣變豬頭柄都肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔一陣就冇事 係柒左D啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db270cbf49e4959f8ccb029317b0048f921c042c","tid":246081,"uid":13317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"有無麻辣火鍋地方推薦"},{"pid":"933b4061433690428b82c04b42bce0f12a9157cf","tid":246081,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"通常返深圳食<br />\n又抵又好食又多野揀"},{"pid":"70d122ee72e9e93232f2917b9d5ff7cac07bbe62","tid":246081,"uid":17064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"辛辣麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36836086d2230e5bf281a1d215d5964bd79e